============================================================================
                            A L S A   T R A Y
============================================================================
  WEBSITE:  http://software.flogisoft.com/alsa-tray/
  VERSION:  0.2
  REALISED:Fri, 22 Oct 2010 17:05:32 +0200 
============================================================================

  ALSA Tray provides a tray icon for setting the volume of the ALSA
  Master mixer

  Dependencies:
	* [Needed  ] pyAlsaAudio <http://pyalsaaudio.sourceforge.net/>
    * [Optional] PyGTK 2.x <http://pygtk.org/>
	  PyGTK is optional for using ALSA Tray with CLI, but it is needed for
	  having a systray icon.
	* [Optional] DBus Python <http://cgit.freedesktop.org/dbus/dbus-python/>
	* [Optional] pyNotify <http://www.galago-project.org/>

  Usage:
    run 'alsa-tray' for launching ALSA Tray in systray
    run 'alsa-tray --help' for help with CLI otions

  Install:
    For install ALSA Tray, run './install.sh --install' as root.

  Uninstall:
    For uninstall ALSA Tray, run './install.sh --remove' as root.

============================================================================

